%p
  This wizard will help you create new <strong>capital projects</strong>.
%p
  The wizard will take you through a series of <strong>five</strong> steps that will help you define the capital project and its scope.
%p
  Before you get started make sure that:
  %ul
    %li your inventory is <strong>up-to-date</strong> and any assets that will be replaced or rehabilitated have been identified.
    %li that you have all of the relevant information about the capital project that you plan to undertake including the TEAM scope.
%p
  Once the wizard has finished you will be able to add activity line items, and identify the assets from your inventory that will be replaced, purchased, or improved.
  